728064f-a.title: Queens: Sutphin Boulevard - 109th Avenue
728064f-a.text:
Sutphin Boulevard, east side, between 109th Avenue and
Arlington Terrace, showing an old private mansion in rear of
St. Josephs Roman Catholic Church. It was for a time the
Church rectory.
March 30, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

728063f-a.text:
Sutphin Boulevard, east side, between 109th Avenue and Arlington
